{"tid":1168090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（有酬）有無巴絲係街見到或者執到隻布甸狗公仔","createTime":"2019-05-23T12:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T14:41:35.000Z","uid":38465,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2d59255eabc65e5d098e21c0799b62e2fcf10f78","tid":1168090,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:38:17.000Z","msg":"多謝各位巴絲入黎呢個post，我都知機會好 渺茫，但都想試下方法，原因係我都唔知幾時唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但呢個公仔對我同女朋友都好緊要<br />\n<br />\n布甸狗公仔<br />\n大細約手掌size<br />\n特點係佢有條繩，類似掛飾設計<br />\n事發時間係星期一，打過去晒所有去過既地方都無消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以係連登睇下有冇可能性<br />\n<br />\n下面係行過路線<br />\n行過路線，由愉景灣廣場，到愉景灣碼頭坐船到中環ifc，再坐西鐵去到圓方，然後就搭車去到天水圍新北江，如果巴打去過上面其中一個地方見到，應該係我個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後再多謝巴絲肯睇曬"},{"pid":"53d7e77375e03fb3299ad7221f8e3c2228737896","tid":1168090,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:43:05.000Z","msg":"你一早講出嚟都有機會今日已經星期四有 去咗堆填區"},{"pid":"a222a122b5b02be97c69e916d563f39f429db8d3","tid":1168090,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53d7e77375e03fb3299ad7221f8e3c2228737896","tid":1168090,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:43:05.000Z","msg":"你一早講出嚟都有機會今日已經星期四有 去咗堆填區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:54:26.000Z","msg":"我都知架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過一開始真係徬徨，靜係識打電話去去過既地方，最後都係無"},{"pid":"e4c8242d14bd1523235dab526261f902b64a213c","tid":1168090,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T14:49:18.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"574f594c5f50daca310c38ac0c482ab93cb6fbdb","tid":1168090,"uid":44055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87e4526a8a9081643667b97e6bfe314c21f98837","tid":1168090,"uid":38465,"like":0,"d